\imt1 Ekamanin
\ip \bk Enno'sa' Kareta Isens Win…®paino\bk* esi iku'to' pe auro'kan n…®to' am âran â'sa' menukasa', ‚Äú12 kaisaron kon iko' am â' t âpataron kon koro'taw…®r…® iye'ta'n â'sa' kon enakan.‚Äù Imenukanin uya k…®po'po'nan kuru r…® main ekamanin apur…®sa' auro'kan n…®to' enpoikanin pe iku'to' pe auro'kan n…®to' p…®', pu'ket â p…®' m…®r…® awonsi'k…® K âri'san pe e'n…®to' eseru m…®r…® awonsi'k…® ato'. K âri'san pe e'n…®to' win…® …®'si'taino p…®' isauro'sa' se warai'nan p…®', imaminke' pe m…®r…® awonsi'k…® …®'r…® p âra r…® entu'ma' r…® e'n…®to' p…®', …®ri uya mo'kan n…®to', wak â pe ato', …®sewaruma'ke' pe, apur…®to' m…®r…® awonsi'k…® ikup â, ani apur…®to', pu'ket â, …®sip…®' e'n…®, m…® pe e'ku'n…®to', m…®r…® awonsi'k…® m…® pe te'ku'sen pe p âra e'n…®to', t âron kon eseru aimenka, utapur…®n n…®to' t âuseta'kai' p âra e'n…®to', m…®r…® awonsi'k…® …®p âreman n…®to' p…®' isauro'sa'.
\ip Enno'sa' kareta uya kuru an ânp…®t â usennakan pe p âra ikup â esi apur…®to' pokon pe, K âri'san pe e'n…®to' ekareei yau.
\iot Iyawon Ekamanin
\io1 Ekamanin (1:1)
\io1 Apur…®to' m…®r…® awonsi'k…® pu'ket â (1:2-8)
\io1 ∆ó'r…® p âra entu'ma' e'n…® m…®r…® awonsi'k…® mamin (1:9-11)
\io1 I'tun m…®r…® awonsi'k…® i'tup…®'n…®to' (1:12-18)
\io1 Eta m…®r…® awonsi'k…® ikup â (1:19-27)
\io1 Panaman tenu yawon ke e'n…® namai' (2:1-13)
\io1 Apur…®to' m…®r…® awonsi'k…® it ârawasooi (2:14-26)
\io1 K âri'san m…®r…® awonsi'k…® iyani (3:1-18)
\io1 K âri'san m…®r…® awonsi'k…® non (4:1‚Äî5:16)
\io1 Iu'mat â pe …®'si'taino tu'kan ku'to' p…®' r…® auro'kan n…®to' (5:7-20)
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Isens, Papa m…®r…® awonsi'k…® Itepuru Sises K ârai poitor â win…®paino,\x - \xo 1:1 \xt Ma'siu 13:55; Ma' 6:3; Inkup â'p â 15:13; Kare'siya 1:19\x*
\p 12 kaisaron kon iko' am â' t âpataron kon koro'taw…®r…® iye'ta'n â'sa' kon enakan: Miyar…®'nokon.
\s1 I'tun N…®to' M…®r…® Awonsi'k…® I'tup…®' N…®to'
\p 
\v 2 Utonpa ton, pori' pe kuru e't…®', tu'kan n…® …®'si'taino ton i'tup…®'n…®to' uye'sa' a'tai …®pona'nokon,
\v 3 ap âne p âra i'tu auya'nokon apur…®to' auya'nokon i'tup…®'to' uya iyannaw…®r…® ut…®n n…®to' kup â.
\v 4 Entakato' t ât ârawasooi i'ma'kai, iyak â'p âsa' pe m…®r…® awonsi'k…® iyenuka'sa' pe …®wesi kon pa, …®'r…® i'se p âra r…®.
\v 5 Ipu'ket â p âra …®tonpa kon esi yau, Papa p…®' nekama'poi, it ânin am âre' pe p âra esii'ma tanporon kon ena', irepa iya r…® m…®r…®, ip…®' t âusakorotai' p âra.
\v 6 E'tane apur…®i'ma nekama'poi ikasimai'ma p âra, ap âne p âra k âr…® r…® ikasimai'ma ekama'ponin esi m…®r…® sipa'sipa parau po, pese't…® n âposi'man â n âpininpan â kasa.
\v 7 K âr…® r…® ka'pon k â'senuminkanin …®'r…® eporo t âuya Itepuru win…®pai tukai';
\v 8 ikasimanin pe kuru iyesi m…®r…®, inkup ân â esi m…®r…® petenan pe p âra.
\p 
\v 9 Entu'manin akon wann…® ne'kup âi m…® pe eke yau tesi p…®'.
\v 10 E'tane imaminke' ne'kup âi m…® pe aiko pe tenasa' p…®', ap âne p âra wana' ip âr â uma'ta kasa ima'tato' oton.
\v 11 Ap âne p âra w âi enu uyep â punin ta'net â a'k…®r…®, m…®r…® uya ite' seketan âk â; itip âr â uta'mo'ka, m…®r…® awonsi'k…® itakor âwanooi uma'ta. M…®r…® kasa imaminke' uma'ta t ât ârawasooi kup â iya koro'tau.\x - \xo 1:11 \xt Aisaya 40:6-7 (LXX)\x*
\p 
\v 12 Pori' k âr…® r…® ka'pon ti'tup…®'to' entakanin, uko'man n…®to' ar âkooi, k âron tato' epoto' iya oton, Papa nekama'p â kamoro ti'n ânkanin nan p…®'.
\p 
\v 13 ‚ÄúPapa uya i'tup…®'n…®to' ya' ut âsa',‚Äù k â'kanin …®n â' r…® i'tup…®'n…®to' ya' te't âsa' a'tai, ap âne p âra Papa esi i'tup…®'nin pen …®ri ke, …®n â' r…® i'tup…®'nin pen k âr…® r…®;
\v 14 e'tane ka'pon e't âr â i'tup…®'n…®to' ya' …®ri i'se iye'to' win…®, m…®r…® uya r…® ipi'sik â m…®r…®pan epori'ma …®ri p…®'.
\v 15 M…®r…® a'tai si, …®ri i'se te'sen entusa' a'tai, …®ri ton eseru ku'nin pe, m…®r…® awonsi'k…® si m…®r…® …®ri ton eseru usemo'kasa' a'tai, uma'tan n…®to' ya' ar…® iya.
\p 
\v 16 K…®senku't…®t âu, utonpa ton n â'kw…®.
\v 17 Tanporon wak â ton m…®r…® awonsi'k…® ipan n…® wak â ton repan n…®to' esi ka'tawin…® t âuye'sen ka' a'kwarii K âip ân â win…®pai, t âusensimasen pen a'kwar â'p â usensimap…®t â kasa.
\v 18 Teseru poro ne'n…®sa' iya i'napairon main aw…®r…®, tanporo wapiyaro' kon inkap â'san imunk…® am â' pe\f + \fr 1:18 \fq wapiyaro' kon inkap â'san imunk…® am â' pe; \ft m…®r…® pe p âra, \fq imunk…® am â' pe kuru r…®\ft ‚ÄîKiri' n âmenuka'p â uya, \fq wapiyaro' kon inkap â'san \ft ta. Main, Mosi' winon uya enupan …®'r…® am â' …®m ârewato' ton m…®r…® awonsi'k…® kiyari ak â'p âsa' an âm â e'sara't…® esi Papa iwano' pe kuru r…®, m…®r…®pan esi itenawon pe kuru tasa'.\f* usen n…®to' kon pe inkap â'san koro'tau.
\s1 Eta M…®r…® Awonsi'k…® Iku'nin Pe E'n…®to'
\p 
\v 19 Utonpa ton n â'kw…®, m…®r…® wenai i'tut…®': T…®w…® tanporon kon ka'pon am â' nesii inke p âra etanin nan pe, t…®n…®n p…®' t âusauro'san pe, m…®r…® awonsi'k…® t…®n…®n p…®' t âusakorotasan pe,
\v 20 ka'pon sakorooi uya Papa e'to' i'se ipokena' pe uko'man n…®to' nep â p âra iyesi.
\v 21 M…®r…® pe iyesi p…®', …®ri eseru m…®r…® awonsi'k…® …®ri inonkat…®' eke pe …®woi'nokon na'ne', m…®r…® awonsi'k…® m…® pe te'ku'se p âra Papa Maimu an ânt…®' …®yewan kon ya', iye'p…®nka'sa' na'ne' ayau'nokon; main …®pika't…®nin kon pe kuru te'sen.
\p 
\v 22 Wak â main aw…®r…® e't…®', etanin pe r…®ken p âra. M…®r…® a'tai, …®iwano' kon pe …®usenku't…® kon pen.
\v 23 ∆ón â' r…® esi a'tai main etanin pe e'tane iku'nin pe p âra, k âr…® r…® esi m…®r…® ka'pon, wanamari ya' tem â' ennin kasa,
\v 24 m…®r…®pan ut…® t âusene'p â t âpo, inke p âra r…® m…®r…® kasa tesi tukai' t âusene'p â pu't…®ka'n âk â iya.
\v 25 E'tane k âr…® ipoi r…® tenu t ât âse wak â main, mo'kanin wann…® ennin m…®r…® awonsi'k…® t âuko'mansen ser…® kup â p…®' t âneta'p â t âpu't…®ka'n â'se p âra e'tane ikup â p…®'‚Äîk âr…® r…® uya wak â epoto' oton m…®r…® t ânkup ân â yau.
\p 
\v 26 ∆ón â' r…® ka'pon esi yau Papa pokon pe t âuko'mansen pe te'ku'sen pe tani mainanpai'ma p âra, k âr…® r…® usenku't…® m…®r…® awonsi'k…® Papa pokon pe iko'manto' napur…®n â esi not ân pe r…®.
\v 27 Wak â kuru esukenan m…®r…® awonsi'k…® imaku'p…® p ân Papa pokon pe uko'man n…®to', Papa, uk âip ân â kon e'to' i'se esi se kasa: piyapaino kon m…®r…® awonsi'k…® itaan'p â ima'tasa' kon t âmainanpai' to' usewankamato' yapai, …®ri ser…® non eseru uya t âma'tan â'to' apai n…®r…® te'mainanpa pe.
\c 2
\s1 Tenu Yawon Ke E'n…® Namai'no
\p 
\v 1 Utonpa ton, a'kwa yawon Uyepuru kon Sises K ârai apur…®nin pe …®wesi kon koro'tau, tenu yawon ke ke't âu.
\v 2 Ka'pon uyep â pe iyesi yau ayam ârasa' kon koro'ta', kor â pun konekasa' irimuui pe, wak â ya' iyepont…®p…®'sa', m…®r…® awonsi'k…® entu'manin, …®ri r…® nin ipon n…®r…® uyep â.
\v 3 K âr…® kuru wak â pe iyepont…®p…®'sa' kup â auya a'tai wak â pe, ‚ÄúSe kuru wak â ayapon,‚Äù tai'ma ip…®', entu'manin p…®', ‚ÄúM…® air…® e'soto'ka',‚Äù m…®r…® pe p âra, ‚ÄúEreuta' non po u'ta piyau,‚Äù tai'ma. M…®r…® ku'sa' auya'nokon a'tai,
\v 4 iye'menkasa' kon pe p âra pe' me'ku'at âu m…®r…® awonsi'k…® eseru aimenkanin pe …®yenasa' kon, ipoken p âra …®ri pe …®usenuminka kon win…® r…®?
\p 
\v 5 Etat…®', utonpa ton n â'kw…®: Papa uya pe' kamoro pata enu yau entu'manin nan pe te'san an ânsa' p âra nai apur…®to' yau eke pe to' e'to' pe m…®r…® awonsi'k…® isauro'sa' r â'p â, esa' wann…® pe te'to' an ânnin pe ti'n ânkanin nan e'to' pe?
\v 6 E'tane entu'manin nan sapemasa' auya'nokon. Imaminke' ton pen pe' kamoro …®kota'manin kon? Kamoro pen pe' kamoro ko't â ta' …®pi'si'nin kon?
\v 7 Kamoro pen pe' kamoro eke ip…®' …®ye't âsa' kon na'ne' ese' sapema pe t âusauro'san pen?
\p 
\v 8 Eke, Itepuru maimu iye'menukasa' na'ne' itekare yau yaw…®r…® kuru …®wesi kon yau, ‚Äú∆ótonpa i'n ânkak…®, m…®si'n ânkayai'ne' kasa,‚Äù\f + \fr 2:8 \ft Ripaiti'kas 19:18\f* tawon, ipoken …®wesi kon m…®r…®.
\v 9 E'tane tenu yawon ke …®wesi kon yau, aumakoita kon; Main, Mosi' winon uya nin si ama'tan âk â kon m…®r…®, m…®r…® Main i'kw…®'nin pe …®wesi kon p…®'.
\v 10 Ap âne p âra …®n â' r…® tanporo Main yaw…®r…® na'ne' e'tane r…® ita'mo'ka tikin nan yau r…® esi m…®r…® …®ri pe, tanporo r…® i'kw…®'sa' iya pe.
\v 11 Ap âne p âra k âr…® r…®, ‚ÄúIyemari'masa' k âsekumankai,‚Äù\f + \fr 2:11 \ft E'sotas 20:14; Isu'taronomi 5:18\f* tawon uya r…® mar…®, ‚Äú∆ón â' r…® k â'w…®n…®i,‚Äù\f + \fr 2:11 \ft E'sotas 20:13; Isu'taronomi 5:17\f* tasa' esi. Iyemari'masa' ekumankanin pe p âra r…® …®wesi yau, e'tane iw…®sa' auya yau, main i'kw…®'nin pe r…® …®yenasa' m…®r…®.
\p 
\v 12 Asauro't…®' m…®r…® awonsi'k…® iku't…®', kamo Main, mo'kanin wann…® yai, iteseru aimenkato' naimenkaton kon pe,
\v 13 ap âne p âra Papa uya eseru aimenka usenpoikato' oton usentu'man pe p âra k âr…® isentu'masa' r â'p â pen pona. Usentu'man uya eseru aimenka wapiya'ka m…®r…®!
\s1 Tapur…®sen M…®r…® Awonsi'k…® T âku'sen
\p 
\v 14 Wak â pe pe' iyesi, utonpa ton, ka'pon e'kup â yau apur…®to' esa' pe e'tane …®'r…® r…® kup âi'ma p âra? M…®r…® warai pe' apur…®to' uya ipika't…®?
\v 15 Utonpa kon, warawo' m…®r…® pe p âra uri'san esi yau ipon p âra, m…®r…® awonsi'k…® w âi kaisa r…® inan âm ân â iti'kiyari p âra,
\v 16 …®tonpa kon uya ta pe iyesi yau ip…®', ‚ÄúEnta, wak â pe e'k…® ukayai' …®p…®'; ikomi' pe p âra …®ko'mank…®, wak â pe mata're't…®i',‚Äù e'tane …®'r…® kup âi'ma p âra r…® i'se iye'to' p…®', wak â pe pe' iyesi?
\v 17 M…®r…® kasa r…®, apur…®to' esi, ikup â uya isakon â't…® p âra iyesi yau, iyeri'sa' pe r…® iyesi.
\p 
\v 18 E'tane t âron n…® uya ta poken iyesi, ‚ÄúApur…®to' esa' pe …®wesi; iku'to' esa' pe esi,‚Äù ta.
\p E'tane ta uya nin, ‚ÄúAnapur…®n â ikup âi'ma p âra enpoikak…® uyena', m…®r…® awonsi'k…® unapur…®n â ikup âi'ma enpoikato' pe uya …®yena',‚Äù tasa'.
\v 19 Apur…® auya moron tikin nan n…® Papa. Oso! M…®r…® r…® mar…® apur…®nin nan kamoro …®ri a'kwar â ton, …®si'n âk âi'ma ip…®'.
\p 
\v 20 Iya'kwar â p ânon …®m…®r…®'nokon! ∆óni'tupai pe' me'at âu apur…®to' ikup âi'ma p âra e'n…® esi not ân pe?\f + \fr 2:20 \fq not ân pe; \ft m…®r…® pe p âra, \fq iyeri'sa' pe\f*
\v 21 Utamokori kon pe' Ep âra'an p…®' ipokena' e' ta'p â pen pe' inkup â'p â wenai Aisi' t âmu t âsa' iya a'tai, Papa ena' use'man n…®to' apon po?\x - \xo 2:21 \xt Iseneses 22:1-14\x*
\v 22 Ene auya'nokon inapur…®n â m…®r…® awonsi'k…® inkup ân â e't ârawasoma'p â …®si'kaisa r…®, m…®r…® awonsi'k…® inkup ân â uya nin si inapur…®n â enuka'n â'sa' m…®r…®.
\v 23 M…®r…® awonsi'k…® itekare iye'menukasa' nin si uta'ku't…®sa', ‚ÄúEp âra'an uya Papa apur…®'p â, m…®r…® p…®' nin si ipokena' pe te'sen ta,‚Äù\f + \fr 2:23 \ft Iseneses 15:6; 2 K ârono'k âr âs 20:7; Aisaya 41:8.\f* m…®r…® awonsi'k…® Papa tonpa tukai' esa'sa' na'ne'.
\v 24 Ene auya'nokon ka'pon koneka Papa uya wak â pe inkup ân â win…®, inapur…®n â win…® r…®ken pen.
\p 
\v 25 M…®r…® kasa r…®, Reyapu, ekumanp…®' te'sen p…®' ipokena' e' ta'p â inkup â'p â wenai, ama'ai non ense'na it…®sa' kon apont…®sa' iya a'tai, m…®r…®pan kon ennoko'p â iya t âron n…® aw…®r…® p…®' pen pe'?\x - \xo 2:25 \xt Isa'suwa 2:1-21\x*
\v 26 Pun, iya'kwar â p ân esi iyeri'sa' pe kasa, apur…®to' t âku'sen a'k…®r…® p âra esi iyeri'sa' pe r…®.
\c 3
\s1 Ani, Tenupansen Pen N…®
\p 
\v 1 Utonpa ton, ti'sa am â' pe esi i'se ke't âu, ap âne p âra ur…®'nokon enupanin nan pe te'san eseru aimenkato' oton m…®r…® ipan pe …®s…® pe.
\v 2 Tanporo tu'kan yau r…® t âuta'mo'kasan ur…®'nokon. ∆ón â' r…® esi yau ipoken p âra te'sen pe p âra t âusaurok â yau, wak â pe kuru iyesi m…®r…®, t âpun n…® si esa' pe iyesi.
\p 
\v 3 Kaware m âta ya' itewa p â'k â t âsa' a'tai, umaimu kon aw…®r…® iye'to' pe, tanporo r…® kaware ra't…® m…®r…®.
\v 4 M…®r…® pe p âra eke kanau am â' p…®' i'tut…®'. Eke ton pe r…® iye'tane, pana'pan n…® a'setun nar…®n â pe, aiko r…® e'se't…®nin uya e'se't…®, anin e'to' i'se aw…®r…® it…®to' pe.
\v 5 M…®r…® kasa si ani aiko r…® pun p â'k â esi, e'tane eke pe t âutapur…®sen. ∆ósenuminkat…®' eke r…® yu' epo't…® p…®' aiko r…® apo' e'sirinkasa' ke.
\v 6 Ani r…® mar…® esi apo' pe, eke pe r…® …®ri yen pe r…® iyesi upun kon p â'k â pe. Tanporo r…® ka'pon a'si'sa' iya, iko'manto' eseru r…® epo't…®to' pe ikup â iya, m…®r…® awonsi'k…® iyepo't…® r…® apo', ekota'man pata'se' yau.
\p 
\v 7 Tanporon kon n…® o' am â', toron am â', ene am â' m…®r…® awonsi'k…® parau kawon kon n…® ene am â', moro' am â' r…® esi tenupansan pe, m…®r…®pan kon n…® enupankasa' ka'pon uya,
\v 8 e'tane …®n â' uya r…® ani enupanka p âra iyesi. Tereutasen pen n…® …®ri pe kuru r…® iyesi, eke pe r…® eri'n â'kanin paisin yen pe iyesi.
\p 
\v 9 Ani ke uyepuru kon m…®r…® awonsi'k…® uk âip ân â kon apur…®p…®t â, m…®r…® awonsi'k…® m…®r…® ke r…® ka'pon am â' pa'n âk â, Papa waraino kon pe ika'sa' kon.\x - \xo 3:9 \xt Iseneses 1:26\x*
\v 10 M…®r…® r…® m âta apai apur…®p…®'to' m…®r…® awonsi'k…® e'pa'n â'n…®to' epa'ka. Utonpa ton, ser…® k âse'ku'nin!
\v 11 Asa'r…® r…® mar…® pe' wak â m…®r…® awonsi'k…® ine'ne'\f + \fr 3:11 \fq ine'ne', \ft m…®r…® pe p âra \fq i'ne', \ft m…®r…® pe p âra \fq …®s…®. \ft (Ap âne, v. 12 n…®r…® enka'k…®.)\f* tuna epa'ka poken nai m…®r…® r…® mar…® tuna epa'kato' euta yai?
\v 12 Utonpa ton, pi' e' pe' epeta poken nai are' pe, m…®r…® pe p âra k âre' e' pe' epeta poken nai pi' pe? Ine'ne' pe tepa'kasen tuna uya wak â enpa'ka pen n…® n…®r…®.
\s1 Asa'ron T âponaron Ipu'ket â
\p 
\v 13 ∆ón â' nai pu'kena' m…®r…® awonsi'k…® ito'ka'n â'nin …®'koro'tau'nokon? T…®w…® nenpoikai wak â pe t âuko'manto' eseru ke, m…® pe te'ku'se p âra t ânkup ân â ke ipu'ket â win…®pai t âuye'sen.
\v 14 E'tane …®s…® pe …®y…®k…®ntato' kon, am âre' pe …®we'to' kon esi yau …®yewan kon yau, ip…®' katapur…®t âu, m…®r…® pe p âra i'napairon p…®' kasi k âkat âu.
\v 15 M…®r…® waraino r…® ipu'ket â u't…® p âra iyesi Ep ân poi, e'tane non winon n…®, iya'kwar â pen n…®, Makoi winon n…®.
\v 16 ∆ók…®ntan n…®to' m…®r…® awonsi'k…® am âre' pe e'pai e'n…®to' yau, …®siporo p âra e'n…®to', tanporon n…® …®ri r…® ku'to' eporo m…®r…®, m…®r…® yau.
\p 
\v 17 E'tane ipu'ket â, Ep ân poi t âuye'sen esi m…®r…® wapiya kuru esukenan n…®, m…®r…® awonsi'k…® t âusewankamai' p âra e'n…®to', t âusi'n ânkasen, t âron kon ennin, main aw…®ron n…®, …®sentu'kena' r…®, eke r…® wak â ku'nin, te'menkasen pen n…®, m…®r…® awonsi'k…® i'napairon n…®.
\v 18 T âusewankamai' te'san i'n…®'pan â'p…®'nin nan, usewankaman n…®to' yau p âra te'p…®nsan uya ipoken e'n…®to' ak â'p âsa' an âm â.
\c 4
\s1 Papa Ena' E'nonkat…®'
\p 
\v 1 ∆ó'r…® uya epanta'man …®sip…®' e'n…® emapu't…® …®'koro'tau'nokon? Ipan pe i'se …®we'to' kon ayau'nokon na'ne' usewa'noman p…®' yapai pe' iyep â pen m…®?
\v 2 ∆ó'r…® r…® i'se …®wesi kon e'tane eporo auya'nokon p âra iyesi. Iwenai …®ye'w…®n…® kon m…®r…® awonsi'k…® …®'r…® r…® enkuui pe …®wesi kon, e'tane i'se …®we'to' kon eporo auya'nokon poken p âra iyesi. ∆ósip…®' …®wesi kon m…®r…® awonsi'k…® …®yepanta'ma kon. Eporo auya'nokon p âra iyesi, ap âne p âra Papa p…®' ekama'po auya'nokon p âra iyesi p…®'.
\v 3 Ekama'po auya'nokon a'tai, eporo auya'nokon p âra iyesi, ap âne p âra …®ri pe iteseru esii'ma ekama'po auya'nokon, …®neporo'p â kon ma'tan âk â ke ipan pe i'se …®we'to' kon n…® kup â p…®'.
\p 
\v 4 ∆óm…®r…®'nokon temari'masa' kon e'tane tekumasan waraino kon ka'pon am â', i'tu auya'nokon p âra pe' iyesi, or â kup â auya'nokon …®tonpa kon pe a'tai, Papa ewaruma't…® auya'nokon pe iyesi? ∆ón â' r…® or â tonpa pe e'paino ena m…®r…® Papa eyaton pe.
\v 5 M…®r…® pe p âra …®usenuminka kon n…® kat…® iye'menukasa' Papa Maimu uya ta iwenai p âra r…®, ‚ÄúIya'kwar â uyau'nokon iko'manto' pe inkup â'p â esi tiwano' pe r…®ken ui'se'nokon,‚Äù\f + \fr 4:5 \fq Iya'kwar â uyau'nokon iko'manto' pe inkup â'p â esi tiwano' pe r…®ken ui'se'nokon; \ft m…®r…® pe p âra, \fq Papa esi ita'kwar â uyau'nokon iko'manto' pe t ânkaa'p â i'se tiwano' pe r…®ken.\f* tukai'?
\v 6 E'tane eke pe miyar…® par…® wak â nonkasa' iya upona'nokon. M…®r…® p…®', iye'menukasa' Papa Maimu uya ta,
\q1 ‚ÄúPapa uya m…® pe te'ku'sen ewaruma't…®,
\q2 e'tane m…® pe te'ku'sen pen pona wak â nonkasa' t âr â iya,‚Äù\f + \fr 4:6 \ft Ipu'ket â 3:34 (LXX)\f*
\m ta iya.
\p 
\v 7 M…®r…® p…®' si, Papa ena' e'nonkat…®'. Makoi iwa'k â't…®', m…®r…®pan ain ânto' pe …®piyapai'nokon.
\v 8 A'ko pe Papa piya' …®si't…®', a'ko pe …®piya'nokon iye'to' pe. ∆óyemiyat â kon ikumi't…®', t âmakooikena' nan ka'pon am â', m…®r…® awonsi'k…® …®yewan kon ikor âkat…®', ikasimanin ye' ton kuru.
\v 9 Aya'kwar â kon tain ânpai' m…®r…® awonsi'k…® t âuta'kwar âp…®'se, t âuk…®'p…®'n ânp…®'se akarant…®'. Auta'k…®r…®to' kon ensimat…®' t âuta'kwar âp…®'se ukaran n…® pe, pori' pe …®we'to' kon ipan pe …®usewankono'ma kon pe.
\v 10 M…® pe te'ku'sen pe p âra enat…®' Itepuru rau, ayan ânto' kon pe iya.
\p 
\v 11 Utonpa ton, …®tonpa kon p…®' …®ri pe isapema pe t âusauro'se p âra e't…®'. ∆ón â' r…® …®ri pe isapema pe t âtonpa p…®' t âusauro'sen, m…®r…® pe p âra iteseru aimenkanin usaurok â main, Mosi' winon p…®' …®ri pe isapema pe m…®r…® awonsi'k…® iteseru aimenka iya. Main eseru aimenka auya a'tai, iyaw…®r…® …®wesi pen m…®r…®, e'tane iteseru aimenkato' auya po …®yereuta.
\v 12 Moro tikin nan n…®ken Main t ânin m…®r…® awonsi'k…® iteseru aimenkanin esi, k âr…® r…® k âr…® r…® t âmerunt…®r â kenan ipika't…®to' ike m…®r…® awonsi'k…® ima'tan â'to' ike. E'tane si …®m…®r…®‚Äî…®n â' pe …®wesi …®tonpa eseru aimenka pa?
\s1 Awanapairon P…®' Utapur…®n
\p 
\v 13 Ap âne etat…®', …®m…®r…®'nokon, ‚ÄúSer…® pe, m…®r…® pe p âra awanapai r…® se pata, m…®r…® pe p âra m…® pata ya' ut…®n m…®r…®, tikin n…® w âipiya enno'se'na m…®r…® yau, p ârata epoto' kup â p…®' m…®r…® awonsi'k…® p ârata eporo p…®',‚Äù tawon nan kon.
\v 14 I'tu auya'nokon p âra r…® iyesi …®'r…® e'kup â awanapai r…® tukai'. ∆ó'r…® m…® …®uko'manto' kon? ∆óm…®r…®'nokon esi kapuru' pe, aka'ne' pe r…® t âusenpoikasen m…®r…® awonsi'k…® tapasen kasa.\x - \xo 4:14 \xt Ipu'ket â 27:1\x*
\v 15 E'tane ru'ku, ‚ÄúItepuru eseru pe iyesi yau, se, m…®r…® pe p âra m…® kup â p…®', uko'man n…®'nokon m…®r…®,‚Äù tato' auya'nokon pe iyesi.
\v 16 Na'ne' nin esi, m…® pe …®ye'kup â kon m…®r…® awonsi'k…® autapur…® kon. Tanporo ser…® waraino utapur…®n esi …®ri pe.
\v 17 ∆ón â' r…®, wak â t ânkup ân â i'tunin, ikup â iya p âra na'ne' umakoita m…®r…®.
\c 5
\s1 Imaminke' Ton Panamato'
\p 
\v 1 Ap âne etat…®', …®m…®r…®'nokon imaminke' ton, akarant…®' m…®r…® awonsi'k…® t âuk…®'p…®'n ânp…®'se akarant…®', ap âne p âra usewankaman n…®to' uye'n…® p…®' man …®pona'nokon.
\v 2 ∆óimamin kon a'motasa' man, ene am â' uya …®pon kon …®'sa' man.
\v 3 ∆ókor â âi kon m…®r…® awonsi'k…® …®sir âpaai kon ukaranp…®'sa' man. Ser…® ikaranp…®'sa' uya apa'n âk â kon m…®r…®, m…®r…® awonsi'k…® …®pun kon an…® iya apo' kasa. Eke pe kuru …®imamin kon am âran â'sa' auya'nokon ser…® iweyu ton u'mat â yau.\x - \xo 5:3 \xt Ma'siu 6:19\x*
\v 4 Ent…®'! Amainar â kon yau iye't ârawasomasa' kon epe'p â, to' e'ma'p â auya'nokon p âra na'ne' ike ukaran n…® p…®' man apa'n âk â kon pe. ∆ói'kiyari kon ak â'p âsa' an ânnin n â'san ukaram â uya Merunt…® pe kuru te'sen ye' Itepuru pana eposa' man.\x - \xo 5:4 \xt Isu'taronomi 24:14-15\x*
\v 5 ∆óuko'mansa' kon man ser…® non po eke pe r…® …®imamin kon tepose, m…®r…® awonsi'k…® ipan pe i'se …®we'to' kon kup â p…®'. ∆óyeka'p…®'sa' kon …®w…®n…® kon weyu a'taino pe.\f + \fr 5:5 \fq …®w…®n…® kon weyu a'taino pe; \ft m…®r…® pe p âra, \fq enta'nan weyu a'taino kasa.\f*
\v 6 ∆óri ku'nin n â'san pen n…® eno'ma'p â m…®r…® awonsi'k…® t â'ka'p â auya'nokon, …®yewa'nomanin kon pokena' nan pen n…®.
\s1 T âuseta'kai' P âra E'n…®to'
\p 
\v 7 M…®r…® p…®' si, t âuseta'kai' p âra e't…®', utonpa ton, Itepuru uyep â p â'k â pona r…®. Ap âne temaina't…®sen ent…®': tenuri'sen non uya epe'kena' kiyari epetan âk â enup…®k…®r…®, t âuseta'kai' p âra te'sen tuna e'sara't…® m…®r…® awonsi'k…® tuna iu'mat â yawon enup…®k…®r…®.
\v 8 ∆óm…®r…®'nokon n…®r…® t âuseta'kai' p âra e't…®', pana' pe e'soto'kat…®', ap âne p âra a'ko pe Itepuru uye'to' man.
\v 9 ∆ótonpa kon p…®' te'naip…®'se p âra, utonpa ton, …®yeseru kon kuru nin aimenka m…®r…®. Eseru aimenkanin man m âra'ta nau r…® iye'soto'kasa'!
\p 
\v 10 Utonpa ton, t âuseta'kai' p âra e'n…®to' ento' ip…®' …®s…® moronka a'taino pe, pu'kena' am â' ent…®', isauro'sa' kon Itepuru ese' yau.
\v 11 Mi'tuyat âi'ne' kasa r…®, ip âremasa' pe to' esi ta, kamoro imoronkanin n â'san p…®'. Isopu uya imoronkasa' r â'p â etasa' auya'nokon, m…®r…® awonsi'k…® iu'mat â pe ene'p â Itepuru n âkup â'p â r â'p â. Itepuru esi eke pe t âusentu'masen m…®r…® awonsi'k…® aiko tawon n…®.\x - \xo 5:11 \xt Isopu 1:21-22; 2:10; Eren 103:8\x*
\p 
\v 12 M…®r…® entai kuru, utonpa ton, …®nku'ton kon p…®' ausaurok â kon a'tai Ep ân k âsesa't âu, m…®r…® pe p âra non n…®, m…®r…® pe p âra …®'r…® r…®. T…®w…®, ‚ÄúEwai',‚Äù tato' auya'nokon nesii, ewai' pe r…®; ‚ÄúKane,‚Äù tato' auya'nokon nesii, kane pe r…®, …®yeno'ma kon kuru nin m…®r…®.\x - \xo 5:12 \xt Ma'siu 5:34-37\x*
\s1 Apur…®to' Yau ∆óp âreman N…®to'
\p 
\v 13 ∆ótonpa kon n…® na'k…® nai ekam ân yau? T…®w…® n…®p âremai. ∆ón â' r…® pe' nai pori' pe? T…®w…® apur…®p…®'to' eremu yai n âserenkai.
\v 14 ∆ótonpa kon n…® na'k…® nai takuru'ke? T…®w…® so'si epuru ton k…®'mai t âpona to' …®p âremato' pe, m…®r…® awonsi'k…® t âkarapaimato' pe Itepuru ese' yau.\x - \xo 5:14 \xt Ma' 6:13\x*
\v 15 Apur…®to' yau iy…®p âremasa' uya takuru'kenan epi't…® m…®r…®; Itepuru uya r…® i'm â'sa'ka. Imakoitasa' pe iyesi yau, ip…®' r…® usentu'man.
\v 16 M…®r…® pe iyesi p…®', …®tonpa kon p…®' r…® amakooi kon ekamat…®', m…®r…® awonsi'k…® …®tonpa kon pona r…® …®p âremat…®', …®usepi't…® kon pa. Ipokena' e' pe te'sen ka'pon …®p ârema esi m…®r…® ipan pe merunt…® pe m…®r…® awonsi'k…® t âwotori'p…® ke.
\p 
\v 17 Iraisa esi'p â ka'pon uwarai'nokon n…®. Iy…®p ârema'p â t âuta'kwar âp…®'se, tuna uyep â p âra iye'to' pe, tuna uyep â p âra si iyesi'p â non amankanin pe osor âwawon pona a'sa'm âyai w âipiya air…® r…®.\x - \xo 5:17 \xt 1 Kin Am â' 17:1; 18:1\x*
\v 18 Iy…®p âremakaa'p â kanan, m…®r…® a'tai ka' awonsi'k…® si tuna uyee'p â, m…®r…® awonsi'k…® si non uya kiyari epetan âk â'p â.\x - \xo 5:18 \xt 1 Kin Am â' 18:42-45\x*
\v 19 Utonpa ton, tikin n…® r…® …®tonpa kon utano'ma pe iyesi yau i'napairon apai, m…®r…® awonsi'k…® t âron n…® uya ina'po,
\v 20 se nesii …®yenu kon yau: ∆ón â' uya r…® t âmakooikenan na'po ipokenan pen apai uya ipika't…® m…®r…® ima'tato' apai, m…®r…® awonsi'k…® tu'kan n…® makooi n…®pont…® iya m…®r…®.\x - \xo 5:20 \xt Ipu'ket â 10:13; 1 Pi'ta 4:8\x*
